"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104orx1701663500155.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/orx1701663500155.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/orx1701663500155.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"orx1701663500155\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code> file defines the syntax of properties as well as\n\t\tproperty groups for web widgets. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"orx1701663500155__section_bg5_hkr_qzb\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"orx1701663500155__note_oln_3kr_qzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code> file is a\n\t\t\t\t\tuser-editable file. You can clone and create your own\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code> file as per your need.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"orx1701663500155__section_e3j_jkr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d785542e67\">Default location</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Depends on the value specified by the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/adm</span> switch. The\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">web.ini</code> file is located in <code class=\"ph codeph\">/uniface/adm</code> in\n\t\t\t\tyour Uniface installation folder.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"orx1701663500155__section_r5x_lkr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d785542e85\">File Sections</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"orx1701663500155__ul_d1p_nkr_qzb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfp1701664033439.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfp1701664033439.html\" title=\"This section, of which multiple are defined in the uproperties.ini file, defines a single property definition used by the Property Inspector of the DSP Component Editor in the IDE.\">[PropertyDefinition]</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmz1701664101486.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmz1701664101486.html\" title=\"This section, as defined in the uproperties.ini file, defines one or more property datatypes to be used by property definitions, where each line is a single datatype definition. The property datatype defines the user interaction for a property in the Property Inspector of the DSP Component Editor in the IDE.\">[PropertyDataTypes]</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fca1701664154061.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fca1701664154061.html\" title=\"This section, as defined in the uproperties.ini file, defines one or more property groups which can be used by property definitions instead of (multiple) lists of individual properties. Each line specifies a single property group. Property groups are used for easy reference, for example when several widgets share the same group of properties.\">[PropertyGroups]</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5444706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5444706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uproperties.ini Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets. Note: The uproperties.ini file is a user-editable file. You can clone and create your own uproperties.ini file as per your need. Default location Depends on the value specified by the /adm switch. The web.ini file is located in /uniface/adm in your Uniface installation folder. File Sections [PropertyDefinition] [PropertyDataTypes] [PropertyGroups] Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}